<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

    <title>NUSCloud</title>
    <% include common-links.ejs %>
    <link href="/styles/homepage.css" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>

  <body>
    <% include public-navbar.ejs %>
	<div id="headerwrap">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<h1>Build NUS Apps<br/>
					Faster. Easier. <b>Better</b>.</h1>
					<a class="btn btn-default btn-lg" href="/login">Login</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-warning btn-lg" href="/registration">Register</a>
				</div>
				<div class="col-lg-6">
					<img class="img-responsive" src="/img/cloud.png" alt="">
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="container">
		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
				<h1>NUSCloud</h1><h3>A collaborative backend platform.</h3>
            </div>
		</div>

		<div class="row mt centered">
			<div class="col-lg-3">
				<img src="/img/storage.png" width="180" alt="">
				<h4>Easy login and storage</h4>
				<p>Add user authentication and data storage with ease using our Javascript SDK to allow access across devices and locations</p>
			</div>

			<div class="col-lg-3">
				<img src="/img/build.png" width="180" alt="">
				<h4>Build on top of others</h4>
				<p>Don't reinvent the wheel - use user data generated by other NUS apps to improve user experience in your application</p>

			</div>

			<div class="col-lg-3">
				<img src="/img/boost.png" width="180" alt="">
				<h4>Boost the app ecosystem</h4>
				<p>Make data generated available via api to other applications to boost the ecosystem and speed up development in NUS</p>
			</div>

            <div class="col-lg-3">
                <img src="/img/control.png" width="180" alt="">
                <h4>Return control to the user</h4>
                <p>Use Oauth2.0 protocol permission infrastructure to enforce user permissions and ensure that the user controls his/her data</p>
            </div>


		</div>
	</div>


	<div class="container">
		<hr>
		<div class="row centered">
			<div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
                <h4>NUSCloud is in Beta</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="col-lg-3"></div>
		</div>
	</div>

